About VOID IDE

VOID
BROWSER IDE v15

VOID is a fully offline, browser-based IDE with a virtual filesystem, Monaco editor, and a powerful asset bundler that lets you run HTML/CSS/JS projects entirely within the browser â€” no server required.

Features: VFS with IndexedDB/LocalStorage/Memory/Real Folder storage, JS module bundling, CSS inlining, binary asset embedding, fetch() bridge, live reload, ZIP import/export, and the new fetch pre-loader that resolves fetch() calls in JS files to blob URLs before execution.

Monaco Editor: 0.44.0 BrowserFS: 2.0.0 JSZip: 3.10.1 Storage: â€”
